name: BUSINESS OF WAR
description:
Stop the war. Stop all this pain. Innocent people are dying. Stop this rich polititian bullsh*t. Stop sending young people to fight for your stupid problems.🙅‍♂️🛑💣💥 Us, as citizens, don't actually care about all your sh*t. We just want to work and live in peace. Don't add more troubles to our lives already full of problems. As always, worker class will pay for all this sh*t. We don't care about if they are nazis, or imperialists, or nothing. Stop playing monopoly with your sh*tty nursery kids analysis please.
Sometimes i just think about our total extinction. All planet would heal and nature would take over to all the harm we did to Earth 🌱
